WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.504
After admin approval, the confirmation link unlocks receipt review and payment.

00:00:03.504 --> 00:00:07.008
Review rental total, insurance, deposit, dates, vehicle, and booking code before charging.

00:00:07.008 --> 00:00:10.512
The customer continues to the secure payment form only after approval.

00:00:10.512 --> 00:00:14.016
Open payment form.

00:00:14.016 --> 00:00:17.520
Payment is now the provider step. If this fails, check payment provider and webhooks before retrying.
